commit.message: Now is a presentable form for the Devpost and judging.
The database now has the savedOnData, where the dads can pop the image in their activity.
Child MVP, now, really, ready. The application is able to delete the node on the database, where the ParentActivity should intercept.
MVP for the child side of things are now done.
Was able to convert the hours to milliseconds.
Was able to populate list of prizes on to list.
Now I have Views those can be cycled through.
Was able to center the button.
